Type: Package
Package: scMMR
Title: Single-Cell Multi-Task Model in R
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R:
    person("Yuhao", "Ouyang", , "ouyang@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A comprehensive toolkit for single-cell RNA-seq analysis powered
    by PyTorch multi-task deep neural networks. Provides joint cell type
    classification and embedding regression, bulk RNA-seq deconvolution with
    cell type proportion estimation, and gene importance attribution via
    Integrated Gradients. Includes pathway enrichment analysis (GSEA, SCPA),
    perturbation ranking with distribution-distance metrics (Wasserstein, MMD),
    pseudotime trajectory analysis, cellular potency prediction (CytoTRACE 2),
    quality control (doublet detection), and a rich visualization suite.
    Supports Seurat objects, h5ad, and matrix inputs with optional GPU (CUDA)
    acceleration.
